title: Star Trek: Voyager - Elite Force + XP (Mac)
description:
This is my release of Star Trek: Voygager - Elite Force + Expansion Pack for MAC


Elite Force is a old game but still big fun :D

Please only download if you have the original of the Game. There is a native port of this Game but only for Classic (Mac OS 7-9).
After you copied the files you have to enter a key to use online gaming.

Known Bugs:
- If you change the graphic settings the program will terminate
- Resolutions are set to 1024x768 and 1280x1024

Have Fun & save the Voyager ;)
